 The philosopher George Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel considers it a rational process towards completion. 

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:33.560
 To avoid the misinterpretation of the "end of history", Hegel was not predicting the end of the world. 

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:40.240
 But to find out what he meant, we must first ask ourselves "What is history?" 

00:00:40.740 --> 00:00:42.220
 According to Hegel, 

00:00:42.660 --> 00:00:48.420
 History is the evolution of perception through confrontation and conflict to a large extent. 

00:00:52.380 --> 00:00:55.940
