00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:23.600
 But these changes do not occur randomly. 

00:01:24.060 --> 00:01:29.700
 For Hegel, history is driven forward by freedom, the essential nature of humankind. 

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:36.460
 As history progresses, we become more conscious, and therefore more rational, 

00:01:36.460 --> 00:01:39.040
